;; Minimal deps.edn for `bbin install`. bbin's generated shim uses
;; `clojure.tools.deps` with `--config`/`:local/root`, which requires a
;; deps.edn manifest at the project root. Runtime deps (clj-yaml, etc.)
;; ship bundled with babashka and live in bb.edn alongside :bbin/bin.
;;
;; `resources` is on :paths so `knot serve` can resolve its static UI
;; bundle from the classpath via `io/resource`. bb.edn mirrors this for
;; the in-tree `bb knot` task; both must list both paths.
{:paths ["src" "resources"]}
